StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCarShipperData]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @Org_Id int, @BeginYear int, @BeginMonth int, @ToYear int, @ToMonth int ) AS BEGIN
DECLARE @datBeginDate as DateTime DECLARE @datToDate as DateTime
SET @datBeginDate = CAST(CAST(@BeginMonth as varchar) + '/1/' + CAST(@BeginYear as varchar) as date.me)
-- Calculate the "to" date by .rst se.ng the date to be the .rst of the month following the ToMonth/ToYear; Then subtract one day SET @datToDate = CAST(CAST((@ToMonth) as varchar) + '/1/' + CAST(@ToYear as varchar) as date.me) SET @datToDate = DateAdd(Month, 1, @datToDate) SET @datToDate = DateAdd(day, -1, @datToDate)
SELECT ORG_ID, sum(RMNPS_OBJECTIVE) as RMNPS_OBJECTIVE, sum(RFNPS_OBJECTIVE) as RFNPS_OBJECTIVE, sum(RESMG_OBJECTIVE) as RESMG_OBJECTIVE, sum(RESMA_OBJECTIVE) as RESMA_OBJECTIVE, sum(RESF_OBJECTIVE) as RESF_OBJECTIVE, sum(PS_OBJECTIVE) as PS_OBJECTIVE, sum(TOTAL_OBJECTIVE) as TOTAL_OBJECTIVE,
sum(RMNPS_ACHIEVED) as RMNPS_ACHIEVED, sum(RFNPS_ACHIEVED) as RFNPS_ACHIEVED, sum(RESMG_ACHIEVED) as RESMG_ACHIEVED, sum(RESMA_ACHIEVED) as RESMA_ACHIEVED, sum(RESF_ACHIEVED) as RESF_ACHIEVED, sum(PS_ACHIEVED) as PS_ACHIEVED, sum(TOTAL_ACHIEVED) as TOTAL_ACHIEVED,
sum(RMNPS_MG_I) as RMNPS_MG_I, sum(RFNPS_MG_I) as RFNPS_MG_I, sum(RESMG_MG_I) as RESMG_MG_I, sum(RESMA_MG_I) as RESMA_MG_I, sum(RESF_MG_I) as RESF_MG_I, sum(PS_USMC_MG_I) as PS_USMC_MG_I, sum(TOTAL_MG_I) as TOTAL_MG_I,
sum(RMNPS_MG_II) as RMNPS_MG_II, sum(RFNPS_MG_II) as RFNPS_MG_II, sum(RESMG_MG_II) as RESMG_MG_II, sum(RESMA_MG_II) as RESMA_MG_II, sum(RESF_MG_II) as RESF_MG_II, sum(PS_USMC_MG_II) as PS_USMC_MG_II, sum(TOTAL_MG_II) as TOTAL_MG_II,
sum(RMNPS_MG_IIIA) as RMNPS_MG_IIIA, sum(RFNPS_MG_IIIA) as RFNPS_MG_IIIA, sum(RESMG_MG_IIIA) as RESMG_MG_IIIA, sum(RESMA_MG_IIIA) as RESMA_MG_IIIA, sum(RESF_MG_IIIA) as RESF_MG_IIIA, sum(PS_USMC_MG_IIIA) as PS_USMC_MG_IIIA, sum(TOTAL_MG_IIIA) as TOTAL_MG_IIIA,
sum(RMNPS_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as RMNPS_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(RFNPS_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as RFNPS_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(RESMG_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as RESMG_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(RESMA_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as RESMA_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(RESF_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as RESF_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(PS_USMC_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as PS_USMC_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA, sum(TOTAL_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA) as TOTAL_TOTAL_MG_I_IIIA,
sum(RMNPS_MG_IIIB) as RMNPS_MG_IIIB, sum(RFNPS_MG_IIIB) as RFNPS_MG_IIIB, sum(RESMG_MG_IIIB) as RESMG_MG_IIIB, sum(RESMA_MG_IIIB) as RESMA_MG_IIIB, sum(RESF_MG_IIIB) as RESF_MG_IIIB, sum(PS_USMC_MG_IIIB) as PS_USMC_MG_IIIB, sum(TOTAL_MG_IIIB) as TOTAL_MG_IIIB,
sum(RMNPS_MG_IV) as RMNPS_MG_IV, sum(RFNPS_MG_IV) as RFNPS_MG_IV, sum(RESMG_MG_IV) as RESMG_MG_IV, sum(RESMA_MG_IV) as RESMA_MG_IV, sum(RESF_MG_IV) as RESF_MG_IV, sum(PS_USMC_MG_IV) as PS_USMC_MG_IV, sum(TOTAL_MG_IV) as TOTAL_MG_IV,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_TWO) as RMNPS_TOE_TWO, sum(RFNPS_TOE_TWO) as RFNPS_TOE_TWO, sum(RESMG_TOE_TWO) as RESMG_TOE_TWO, sum(RESMA_TOE_TWO) as RESMA_TOE_TWO, sum(RESF_TOE_TWO) as RESF_TOE_TWO, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_TWO) as PS_USMC_TOE_TWO, sum(TOTAL_TOE_TWO) as TOTAL_TOE_TWO,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_THREE) as RMNPS_TOE_THREE, sum(RFNPS_TOE_THREE) as RFNPS_TOE_THREE, sum(RESMG_TOE_THREE) as RESMG_TOE_THREE, sum(RESMA_TOE_THREE) as RESMA_TOE_THREE, sum(RESF_TOE_THREE) as RESF_TOE_THREE, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_THREE) as PS_USMC_TOE_THREE, sum(TOTAL_TOE_THREE) as TOTAL_TOE_THREE,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_FOUR) as RMNPS_TOE_FOUR, sum(RFNPS_TOE_FOUR) as RFNPS_TOE_FOUR, sum(RESMG_TOE_FOUR) as RESMG_TOE_FOUR, sum(RESMA_TOE_FOUR) as RESMA_TOE_FOUR, sum(RESF_TOE_FOUR) as RESF_TOE_FOUR, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_FOUR) as PS_USMC_TOE_FOUR, sum(TOTAL_TOE_FOUR) as TOTAL_TOE_FOUR,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_FIVE) as RMNPS_TOE_FIVE, sum(RFNPS_TOE_FIVE) as RFNPS_TOE_FIVE, sum(RESMG_TOE_FIVE) as RESMG_TOE_FIVE, sum(RESMA_TOE_FIVE) as RESMA_TOE_FIVE, sum(RESF_TOE_FIVE) as RESF_TOE_FIVE, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_FIVE) as PS_USMC_TOE_FIVE, sum(TOTAL_TOE_FIVE) as TOTAL_TOE_FIVE,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_SIX) as RMNPS_TOE_SIX, sum(RFNPS_TOE_SIX) as RFNPS_TOE_SIX, sum(RESMG_TOE_SIX) as RESMG_TOE_SIX, sum(RESMA_TOE_SIX) as RESMA_TOE_SIX, sum(RESF_TOE_SIX) as RESF_TOE_SIX, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_SIX) as PS_USMC_TOE_SIX, sum(TOTAL_TOE_SIX) as TOTAL_TOE_SIX,
sum(RMNPS_TOE_INVALID) as RMNPS_TOE_INVALID, sum(RFNPS_TOE_INVALID) as RFNPS_TOE_INVALID, sum(RESMG_TOE_INVALID) as RESMG_TOE_INVALID, sum(RESMA_TOE_INVALID) as RESMA_TOE_INVALID, sum(RESF_TOE_INVALID) as RESF_TOE_INVALID, sum(PS_USMC_TOE_INVALID) as PS_USMC_TOE_INVALID, sum(TOTAL_TOE_INVALID) as TOTAL_TOE_INVALID,
sum(RMNPS_TIER_ONE) as RMNPS_TIER_ONE, sum(RFNPS_TIER_ONE) as RFNPS_TIER_ONE, sum(RESMG_TIER_ONE) as RESMG_TIER_ONE, sum(RESMA_TIER_ONE) as RESMA_TIER_ONE, sum(RESF_TIER_ONE) as RESF_TIER_ONE, sum(PS_USMC_TIER_ONE) as PS_USMC_TIER_ONE, sum(TOTAL_TIER_ONE) as TOTAL_TIER_ONE,
sum(RMNPS_TIER_TWO) as RMNPS_TIER_TWO, sum(RFNPS_TIER_TWO) as RFNPS_TIER_TWO, sum(RESMG_TIER_TWO) as RESMG_TIER_TWO, sum(RESMA_TIER_TWO) as RESMA_TIER_TWO, sum(RESF_TIER_TWO) as RESF_TIER_TWO, sum(PS_USMC_TIER_TWO) as PS_USMC_TIER_TWO, sum(TOTAL_TIER_TWO) as TOTAL_TIER_TWO,
sum(RMNPS_TIER_THREE) as RMNPS_TIER_THREE, sum(RFNPS_TIER_THREE) as RFNPS_TIER_THREE, sum(RESMG_TIER_THREE) as RESMG_TIER_THREE, sum(RESMA_TIER_THREE) as RESMA_TIER_THREE, sum(RESF_TIER_THREE) as RESF_TIER_THREE, sum(PS_USMC_TIER_THREE) as PS_USMC_TIER_THREE, sum(TOTAL_TIER_THREE) as TOTAL_TIER_THREE,
sum(MALE_SHIP_MCRD) as MALE_SHIP_MCRD, sum(MALE_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD) as MALE_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD, sum(FEMALE_SHIP_MCRD) as FEMALE_SHIP_MCRD, sum(FEMALE_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD) as FEMALE_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD, sum(TOTAL_SHIP_MCRD) as TOTAL_SHIP_MCRD, sum(TOTAL_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD) as TOTAL_I_IIIA_SHIP_MCRD,
sum(MALE_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as MALE_MCRD_DISCHARGE, sum(MALE_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as MALE_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE, sum(FEMALE_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as FEMALE_MCRD_DISCHARGE, sum(FEMALE_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as FEMALE_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE, sum(TOTAL_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as TOTAL_MCRD_DISCHARGE, sum(TOTAL_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE) as TOTAL_I_IIIA_MCRD_DISCHARGE,
max(update_date) as UPDATE_DATE
FROM CAR_SHIPPER WHERE ORG_ID = @Org_Id AND ( (CAST(CAST(RPT_MONTH as varchar) + '/1/' + CAST(RPT_YEAR as varchar) AS DateTime) BETWEEN @datBeginDate and @datToDate) ) GROUP BY ORG_ID END
